<doc id="126320" url="https://af.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=126320" title="Ferdinand Canu">
Ferdinand Canu

Ferdinand Canu (1863-1932) was 'n Franse paleontoloog en skrywer. In 1923 word hy die Daniel Giraud Elliot Medalje toegeken vir sy werk ""North American Later Tertiary and Quaternary Bryozoa"". 




